tournaments.about:
Here are informations about tournament

Important dates:
• Registration: July 19 up to August 3 11:59
• Tournament draw: August 3
• Tournament start: August 4
• Tournament end: Mid-November

Tournament format:
• All players will be divided in 2 groups. Seeding according to the results of previous championship (https://carcassonne.gg/HR-2025-OC/).
• Top 4 from each group will enter the playoffs.
• In each group each pair of players will play one Best of Three (BO3) match together.
• During the draw, all matches will be scheduled for their respective weeks. Each player will be scheduled to play at most one match per week.
• The players must agree on the exact time their match will be played. When agreed, one of the players must fill out a form indicating that time.
• Depending if at least one of the players is Premium, players will play normal game with Slow settings or Tournament format with 15 minutes per player.
• In case of a game ending in a tie, the win goes to the player who has not started (as usual on BGA).
• Final results will be determined by, subsequently, the number of won matches, the difference of games won and lost, and the number of games won. In case of a tie, these criteria will be applied once more, but this time using only the matches between the tied players.

Prizes: The winner will receive the opportunity to represent Croatia in the next Carcassonne Champions League (CCL) season, according to the coefficient update after this year's ETCOC.
